{"word":"H8213 - שָׁפֵל - shâphêl - shaw-fale' - Abase","slug":"H8213","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׁפֵל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>shâphêl"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>shaw-fale'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Abase"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05E4;&#x05DC; - sha&#x0302;phe&#x0302;l</b> - <i>shaw-fale'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>depress</i> or <i>sink</i> (especially figuratively to <i>humiliate</i>, intransitively or transitively): - abase, bring (cast, put) down, debase, humble (self), be (bring, lay, make, put) low (-er)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H8216\">H8216</a>, <a href=\"#/H8217\">H8217</a>, <a href=\"#/H8218\">H8218</a>, <a href=\"#/H8219\">H8219</a>, <a href=\"#/H8220\">H8220</a>, <a href=\"#/H8221\">H8221</a>, <a href=\"#/H8223\">H8223</a>, <a href=\"#/H8224\">H8224</a>, <a href=\"#/H8225\">H8225</a>"}]}